ic+evaluation+of+the+portal+and+hepatic+systems&amp;author=C+Owen&amp;author=P+Meyers&amp;publication_year=2006&amp;journal=J+Diagn+Med+Sonogr&amp;pages=317-328&amp;doi=10.1177%2F8756479306293101">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Roguin A. Christian Johann Doppler: the man behind the effect. <em>Br J Radiol</em> 2002;75(895):615–619.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1259/bjr.75.895.750615">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12145136/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Christian+Johann+Doppler%3A+the+man+behind+the+effect&amp;author=A+Roguin&amp;publication_year=2002&amp;journal=Br+J+Radiol&amp;pages=615-619&amp;doi=10.1259%2Fbjr.75.895.750615&amp;pmid=12145136">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="r8" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Brant WE, Helms CA. Fundamentals of diagnostic radiology. Philadelphia, Pa: <em>Lippincott</em>, Williams &amp; Wilkins, 2007.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Fundamentals+of+diagnostic+radiology&amp;author=WE+Brant&amp;author=CA+Helms&amp;publication_year=2007">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="r9" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Lim AK, Patel N, Eckersley RJ, et al. Can Doppler sonography grade the severity of hepatitis C-related liver disease? <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2005;184(6):1848–1853.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/ajr.184.6.01841848">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15908541/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Can+Doppler+sonography+grade+the+severity+of+hepatitis+C-related+liver+disease%3F&amp;author=AK+Lim&amp;author=N+Patel&amp;author=RJ+Eckersley&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=1848-1853&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.184.6.01841848&amp;pmid=15908541">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">10.</div><div id="r10" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Dietrich CF, Lee JH, Gottschalk R, et al. Hepatic and portal vein flow pattern in correlation with intrahepatic fat deposition and liver histology in patients with chronic hepatitis C. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 1998;171(2):437–443.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/ajr.171.2.9694471">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9694471/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Hepatic+and+portal+vein+flow+pattern+in+correlation+with+intrahepatic+fat+deposition+and+liver+histology+in+patients+with+chronic+hepatitis+C.&amp;author=CF+Dietrich&amp;author=JH+Lee&amp;author=R+Gottschalk&amp;publication_year=1998&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=437-443&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.171.2.9694471&amp;pmid=9694471">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">11.</div><div id="r11" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Scissons R. Characterizing triphasic, biphasic, and monophasic doppler waveforms. <em>J Diagn Med Sonogr</em> 2008;24(5):269–276.</div><div cla